Phase	Focus	Duration	Deliverables
Phase 1	Core workspace — auth, board, notes, chat, activity feed	2–3 weeks	Fully usable by the team, deployed on Vercel
Phase 2	Depth features — task detail, due dates, notifications, search, standups	2–3 weeks	Production-ready, shareable with other teams
